# Hono API Rules

- Use `OpenAPIHono`, `createRoute`, and Zod-backed schemas for endpoints.
- Validate env with a helper instead of reading raw env vars in handlers.
- Success responses should use `{ data: ... }`; failures should use `{ error: ... }`.
- Protected routes should verify bearer auth.
- Keep OpenAPI docs available at `/reference`.
- Use contextual server-side logging and avoid leaking sensitive error details to clients.
